articles.summary:
@lkr I asked Claude Code, what do you have access to, that you probably shouldn’t have access to.

The biggest thing was it could impersonate me. Even run jobs when I’m not at my computer.

Loads of stuff!!  I’m even considering having a separate computer to access production

